fusca - Stands for *f*ast *u*serpsace *s*ynchronized *c*lock *a*dapter

A header-only C++ class for fast user-space access to a slow-to-read clock

Synchronizes a fast-to-read userpsace clock (such as rdtsc) with a slow-to-read 
clock such as PTP or clock_gettime()

The clocks don't need to run at the same rates or use the same units
